[resource]
script = ExtResource("8_riieh")
id = "create_scene"
title = "Create new scene"
description = "**Purpose**
Create a new scene file with a root node based on a specified class.

**Usage notes**
- The `file_path` parameter specifies where the scene will be created.
- The `base_class` parameter determines the type of the scene root node.
- The `scene_root_name` parameter sets the name for the scene root node.
- The file must not exist at the specified path.
- The scene will be created with an empty node hierarchy.
- Missing directories in the `file_path` will be created.

**Example**
file_path: res://scenes/player/Player.tscn
base_class: Node2D
scene_root_name: Player"
category = ExtResource("1_m1fdn")
parameters = Array[ExtResource("6_n04br")]([SubResource("Resource_lm6dm"), SubResource("Resource_rjxom"), SubResource("Resource_7tjv0"), ExtResource("7_g4hxb")])
options = Array[ExtResource("2_11jbr")]([ExtResource("3_asy7v"), ExtResource("4_v07w4"), ExtResource("5_0ef0w")])
